INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS FOR DEV ASSESSMENT

Configuration changes:

1. Change database configuration in /application/config/database.php
   - hostname
   - username
   - password
   - database
   
2. Change base_url in /application/config/config.php
   - $config['base_url'] to your own URL or localhost.
   
3. Change paths to system and application folders in index.php (root directory)